Output demo/tenetx-demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "# Install tenetx globally"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "npm install -g tenetx"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Initialize your philosophy"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "tenetx onboarding"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# Check your environment"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "tenetx doctor"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Start Claude Code with your philosophy"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "tenetx"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# That's it! Your principles now drive your workflow."
Enter
Sleep 2s
